### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@userId = user-123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Create a Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "title": "Complete AWS Serverless Project",
  "description": "Build a CRUD API with Lambda, API Gateway, and DynamoDB"
}

### Get All Tasks (for this user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Get Single Task (replace TASK_ID with actual ID from create response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/TASK_ID
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Update a Task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/TASK_ID
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete a Task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/TASK_ID
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Test with different user (should see empty list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
X-User-Id: different-user-456
